    <item>
      <title>Graduate Student</title>
      <link>/job-posting/graduate-student-2021/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Sep 2020 00:00:01 -0400</pubDate>
      <guid>/job-posting/graduate-student-2021/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I have an opening for a Masters or Ph.D. student to begin in Fall 2021. Please contact me &lt;strong&gt;as soon as possible&lt;/strong&gt; if you are interested in joining the lab using the instructions on the 
&lt;a href=&#34;/join#gradstudents&#34;&gt;Join Us&lt;/a&gt; page.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The application, general information, &amp;amp; deadlines for NCSU grad programs can be found 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://grad.ncsu.edu/programs/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. Most likely to be relevant are the ** program deadlines for 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://grad.ncsu.edu/programs/details/?program=PB&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Plant Biology&lt;/a&gt; (15 January 2021) &amp;amp; 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://grad.ncsu.edu/programs/details/?program=MB&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Microbiology&lt;/a&gt; (1 December 2021)**.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
